Now, these numbers, 18?

50:48.950 --> 50:50.572
They're probably going down.

50:51.753 --> 50:53.014
So how many?

50:53.074 --> 50:55.937
Well, on one level, it's about eight.

50:56.377 --> 50:59.820
On the other, it's two, four, six.

50:59.841 --> 51:00.441
Many levels.

51:00.461 --> 51:01.402
There are more.

51:01.522 --> 51:03.064
It's about 10 or 12 decks.

51:03.404 --> 51:03.784
Decks.

51:04.044 --> 51:05.065
Decks is a key word.

51:05.666 --> 51:05.766
Yeah.

