Really?

51:34.287 --> 51:36.590
Not the mechanized system.

51:36.610 --> 51:39.474
No, but it just goes around.

51:40.035 --> 51:44.241
And we have an old tube system, a message tube system.

51:44.261 --> 51:45.482
Pneumatic tube.

51:45.502 --> 51:48.547
So did you go to library school or something like that?

51:48.827 --> 51:49.167
Ah, Rutgers.

51:49.268 --> 51:49.949
Library school.

