No, it's still there.

51:55.937 --> 52:00.383
It's more, it used to be a Rutgers school library.

52:00.483 --> 52:00.964
Now it's

52:01.467 --> 52:07.894
The communications, the school communications is kind of merged, folded into it.

52:07.914 --> 52:11.017
Now, do you work in the collections management division?

52:11.077 --> 52:11.938
Is that what you're?

52:11.958 --> 52:12.178
Yes.

52:12.278 --> 52:14.020
I just noticed on the side over there.

52:14.040 --> 52:19.666
Yeah, this is kind of part of my division.

52:19.746 --> 52:22.910
It's a large division of about 250 people.

52:23.450 --> 52:25.973
And that's probably down from what it once was.

52:26.375 --> 52:27.396
In some areas.

52:27.416 --> 52:32.583
Yeah, mostly behind the scenes.

52:32.603 --> 52:38.231
Are we still in Jefferson?

52:38.251 --> 52:38.812
Yeah.

52:38.832 --> 52:42.777
I mean, they come here for these books and the multimedia.

52:42.877 --> 52:48.204
But, you know, the books are always in different languages, and this is a key part of research.

52:48.225 --> 52:50.087
You said they're here and they're out of any place else.

52:50.320 --> 52:54.668
A lot of our books, people come here because these things are not anywhere else.

52:55.169 --> 52:59.898
We're a national library, and a lot of our collections you don't find anywhere else.

52:59.958 --> 53:05.669
So therefore, the responsibility that you have is as a depository library.

53:05.769 --> 53:09.175
And not only to people now, but to future generations.

53:09.195 --> 53:11.620
There is no other place to find this material.

53:11.819 --> 53:12.682
In many cases.

53:12.762 --> 53:17.516
So when you look at it and decide if it's going off-site, I don't know which way you're going.

